Package: finnishgrid
Type: Package
Title: Fingrid Open Data API R Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Markus", "Virtanen", email = "markus.m.virtanen@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Kai", "Hippi", email = "kai.hippi@aalto.fi", 
           role = "aut")
  )
Description: R API client package for Fingrid Open Data on the 
    electricity market and the power system. get_data() function
    holds the main application logic to retrieve time-series data.
    API calls require free user account registration.
